<h3>Precipitation</h3>
<br><br>
Figure 11 shows wetter than normal conditions for December over northern and southern parts of Europe with precipitation amounts mostly much above or exceptionally above normal. Drier than normal conditions prevailed over central and parts of eastern Europe (e.g. Romania and Bulgaria).
